Salesperson Information – Verified. Salesperson details appear correctly in the summary.
Required Field Validation – Failed. Create Invoice proceeds with empty Customer Contact, Billing Address, and Salesperson; no error messages shown.
Initial Totals on First Load – Failed. With the default item row untouched, Subtotal/Tax/Shipping/Total display $0.00 instead of the computed amount.
Submit-Time Recalculation – Failed. Clicking Create Invoice without any edits does not trigger a final totals recompute; the Invoice Summary still shows $0.00.
Email regex validation - Failed. Need to Provide error when the email format is incorrect in the Customer Contact field.
Important fileds - Failed. Important fields like Customer Contact, Billing Address, and Salesperson is not showing asterisk to indicate they are mandatory.
Date Auto-Fill on Page Load - Failed. Invoice date does not default to current date automatically.
Date Range Validation -  Failed - User can be able to select a future date for invoice creation which should be restricted.
Scrollable View -  Failed - For long invoices (many items), table is breaking the layout instead of remaining scrollable within the container.
Negative Quantity or Price - Failed - No validation error is displayed when user enters negative or zero quantity/price.
Empty Item Row Prevention - Failed - Invoice submission is allowed even if item rows are empty or incomplete.
Shipping Fee Field Validation - Failed - Shipping fee field is accepting text and negative values.
Tax Calculation Accuracy - Failed - Tax calculation formula and decimal rounding logic is incorrect.
Invoice Reset on Submission - Passed - After “Create Invoice,” form is not clearing or resetting correctly for new entry.